                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">What sort of timers, if any, do people use here?
<br />

<br />
I have seen those fancy shmancy timers that clock every buff/debuff/mez/etc you cast, but are they really worth it?</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://users.adelphia.net/~monolith/adrecia1.jpg" border="0" />
