Sounds like it might be part of the aforementioned ShowEQ widget.
<br />

<br />
That said, I use a standard dial-timer with an incrementing digital counter as well.  It allows me to lazily time things I need to time over long periods (Usually either spawns, or when EB is going to wear off) with the digital timer (which runs for an hour then rolls over) and I can time mezzes with the handy tic-based dial timer. (That allows me to click on a tic to 'mark' it to aid my memory.)
<br />

<br />
The bar timers never really worked out for me - partly because I realized I don't really care that much about when haste is going to wear off.  And since I have inspect buffs 2 now, I care even less. <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
